OL,3,CTwo people arrested over death of 22-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in Hounslow stabbing
OL,6,FA man and a woman have been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder after a 22-year-
OL,8,Fold man was stabbed to death in west
OL,9,FLondon, police have said.
OL,11,FThe suspects, both aged 21, were taken
OL,12,Finto custody on Sunday, according to
OL,13,Fthe Metropolitan Police.
OL,15,FThe victim, named by police as Haruun
OL,16,FHassan, was pronounced dead at the
OL,17,Fscene in Hounslow in the early hours
OL,18,Fof June 30, despite the best efforts
OL,19,Fof paramedics.
