OL,3,CTwo people arrested over death of 22-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in Hounslow stabbing
OL,6,FOfficers had been called at around
OL,7,F1.47am to reports of a stabbing at the
OL,8,Fjunction of Bath Road and Great
OL,9,FSouthwest Road.
OL,11,FThey attended the scene alongside the
OL,12,FLondon Ambulance Service and found Mr
OL,13,FHassan with serious injuries.
OL,15,FHis next-of-kin continue to receive
OL,16,Fsupport from specialist officers,
OL,17,Fpolice have said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
