OL,3,CTwo people arrested over death of 22-
OL,4,Cyear-old man in Hounslow stabbing
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with Haruun's
OL,7,Ffamily during this very difficult
OL,8,Ftime," detective chief inspector Paul
OL,9,FWaller, who is leading the
OL,10,Finvestigation, said.
OL,12,F"Our investigation is progressing and
OL,13,Fwe have made two arrests, with those
OL,14,Fpeople now in custody.
OL,16,F"We continue to ask any witnesses or
OL,17,Fanyone with information about what
OL,18,Fhappened to Haruun that night to
OL,19,Fplease contact us as soon as possible."
